 07 Jul 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://richardcsuwandi.github.io/authors/lei-cheng/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Yiyong Sun</title><link>https://richardcsuwandi.github.io/authors/yiyong-sun/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 Jul 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://richardcsuwandi.github.io/authors/yiyong-sun/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Shuai Wang</title><link>https://richardcsuwandi.github.io/authors/shuai-wang/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 Jun 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://richardcsuwandi.github.io/authors/shuai-wang/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Tsung-Hui Chang</title><link>https://richardcsuwandi.github.io/authors/tsung-hui-chang/</link><pubDate>Tue, 01 Jun 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://richardcsuwandi.github.io/authors/tsung-hui-chang/</guid><description/></item><item><title/><link>https://richardcsuwandi.github.io/authors/admin/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://richardcsuwandi.github.io/authors/admin/</guid><description>&lt;p>I am currently pursuing my PhD in Computer and Information Engineering at the &lt;a href="https://cuhk.edu.cn/en/">Chinese University of Hong Kong, Shenzhen (CUHK-Shenzhen)&lt;/a>, under the supervision of &lt;a href="https://sse.cuhk.edu.cn/en/faculty/yinfeng">Prof. Feng Yin&lt;/a> and &lt;a href="https://sse.cuhk.edu.cn/en/faculty/tsunghuichang">Prof. Tsung-Hui Chang&lt;/a>. Prior to my PhD studies, I obtained my BSc degree in Statistics from CUHK-Shenzhen in 2023.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>I am affiliated with the &lt;a href="https://blsp-group.github.io/">Bayesian Learning for Signal Processing (BLSP) Group&lt;/a> of CUHK-Shenzhen, where my research mainly focuses on Bayesian learning, distributed optimization, and trustworthy machine learning.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>